"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/383826","Ministry of Defence","false","2015-06-23","<p>The Strategic Defence and Security Review will take account of all UK treaty obligations.</p>","Sevenoaks","Michael Fallon",,"2015-06-23T16:20:35.887Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/383826/answer","Biography information for Sir Michael Fallon","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/383826/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/383826/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2015-06-18","Strategic Defence and Security Review","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, which UK treaty obligations will be taken into account in development of the Strategic Defence Review.","false","Biography information for Ian C. Lucas","Wrexham","Ian C. Lucas","3240"
